Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.28,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:03:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates  who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after \NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves \Ncaught up in the turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and involved in an all-out war!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surume!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were doing everything he says \Nin order to save your brother's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your younger brother or older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:04:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me try to save his life too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:37.80,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Noah Closing in! The Fish-Man \NIsland Facing Destruction!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Ship of Promise! "Noah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is doing it and how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit strange,  but \Nwhy are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a relic from history. \NIt serves no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We can't let anything \Nhappen to that ship-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the proper day comes, no one \Nis allowed to move that ship-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he took a lot of Energy \NSteroids and became a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What do you three want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surume!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surume-sama, you are very strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Yowahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what Fish-Man Karate is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His head is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it with a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not gonna work. Because \NI'm made of rubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your skill is nothing compared to Jimbei's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! That's why you \Nshouldn't depend on fake power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head; Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Shell Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Your head's gonna crack open!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:08:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His head was harder than iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armament; Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't get hit at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:09:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he know when they come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Observation Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama, he is unbelievably strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's great! Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:10:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how strong the \Nworld-renowned pirate is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I-Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Noah of the Fish-Man District?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Noah in the air over the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's heading towards this plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost broken through \Nthe bubble around the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the bubble pops, the island is \Nfinished! We're all gonna get washed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is that?!\N--The Noah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the ship hits, the whole \Nisland will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's operating it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it has an engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is that?!\N--It's gigantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know what's happening \Nbut we're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the sea will turn red \Nif we all get smashed at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things like that! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Evacuate!\N--Get into the water off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! I slipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Wadatsumi - working for Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Vander Decken! I fell off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the ship! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decken?! What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is this one of your strategies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Decken is operating the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you good-for-nothings!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How tough can he be?! I attacked \Nhim with the Armament Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say Decken? That crazy pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a part of the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear me, Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Decken threw the Noah \Nlike he threw those letters and axes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been loving you for 10 years \Nsince you were just a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one who could love you \Nlike I do in all the wide world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my love! Love, love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you just accept it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things that I throw with \Nmy Mark-Mark Fruit power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won't stop until they crash into \Nsomething or hit their target!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah the giant ship! It embodies \Nmy love for you! Accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And drop dead along with all the \NFish-Man Island, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Decken! What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wadatsumi! It's too late! It's \Nimpossible for me to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I need you to become a sacrifice upon \NShirahoshi's death, along with the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! The bubble is gonna pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where did Princess Shirahoshi go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? She's not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Princess! Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Shirahoshi disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:17:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Princess Shirahoshi!\N--When did she go up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yowahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi! Why did she do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that ship is flying towards her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then she...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the girl that I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wanted to take just my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am the only one who you want to kill, \Nplease do not harm the other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Princess-sama!\N--Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The Noah is changing its course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:19:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's heading towards \NPrincess Shirahoshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this, Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that crazy Decken bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was gonna crush us all \Nalong with the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he betray us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we do something to save her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How amazingly beautiful you are, \NShirahoshi! Even your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to take the \Nmatter into your own hands
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:20:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to save the country, \Naren't you, Shirahoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shira... hoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're eligible to become Vander \NDecken IX's wife as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better die while you're still \Nbeautiful and live in my heart forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Princess-sama!\N--How could you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't do that!\N--Run, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Yowahoshi! I told her to stick with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Captain Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where did Hordy-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! He's up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's heading for the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me, Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like this idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! How dare \Nhe hurt Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go up there! You stay here \Nand take care of the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.97,0:22:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy, the ship is in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the ship is \Nfilled with water, Jimbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know but I know Decken \Nis a Devil Fruit eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there must be air for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a coral that produces bubbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you to save \Nmy beloved Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:23:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ready, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.68,0:23:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attempting to save Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.88,0:23:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi lures the Noah away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Luffy follows her,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's cornered into an underwater battle \Nat a severe disadvantage against Hordy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Shirahoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to finish things!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hurry up, Luffy! Shirahoshi's \NLife in Jeopardy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
